‼️🎁 GIVEAWAY TIME 🎁‼️
•
Let’s get CREATIVE 🎨 and let your inner ARTIST 👩‍🎨 take over! 🙌🏻 Stand a chance to win A FULL CASE of the LATEST @tokidoki  DIY Unicorno 🦄✨ With just 4 SIMPLE STEPS! 😱 Heres how: •
Step 1️⃣: Must be FOLLOWING us and LIKE this post! 😋 Head over to our IG Story Highlight “DIYGiveaway2020” and SCREENSHOT 📱 the template! ☝🏻
•
Step 2️⃣: Use that template and let YOUR Imagination 🌈 and CREATIVITY 🌟settle the rest! 🤩 Feel FREE to use GIFs & the drawing tools that IG Story offers, so go CRAZY 🤪😉 •
Step 3️⃣: Next, POST it on your IG Story and Tag us at @actioncitysg and @tokidokibrand with the hashtag #unicornogiveaway2020 ! 😇 Please ensure that your account is PUBLIC ☝🏻 so that we can see your works ✨
•
Step 4️⃣: Head on back to this post to TAG 3 of your friends in the COMMENTS section and tell us why you deserve to win! 😉🥳 Don’t forget to SHARE this post around too to get higher chances of WINNING 😜🙌🏻
•
•
So what are you waiting for?! 😋 Start getting CREATIVE! 🌈 Contest ends on 06/06, Saturday at 12PM Sharp. Winners will be announced via @actioncitysg Instagram and Facebook in the same month. 🥳🦄 T&Cs apply.
